  <title>Cloud API feature Matrix</title>

  <para>Existing APIs for IaaS based Clouds already fulfill some of the Use
  cases and also address some requirements. The following list of APIs have
  been evaluated during the creation of the OCCI working group process.</para>

  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>OCCI - Open Cloud Computing Interface</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
      <para>EC2 - Amazon Elastic Compute Cloud</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
      <para>EH - ElasticHosts</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
      <para>FS - Flexiscale</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
      <para>GG - GoGrid</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
      <para>SC - Sun Cloud API</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
      <para>CS - Rackspace Cloud Servers</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
      <para>VM - WMware vSphere</para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>

